332
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:24,340
Don't.

333
00:23:25,510 --> 00:23:26,310
Mr. Yan.

334
00:23:27,130 --> 00:23:27,680
Don't go.

335
00:23:27,820 --> 00:23:28,250
You...

336
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:30,290
Do you expect

337
00:23:30,290 --> 00:23:31,850
me to just stand by and watch my cousin

338
00:23:31,850 --> 00:23:33,650
