339
00:23:33,790 --> 00:23:35,030
Can't you see?

340
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,000
The Yang family is naturally treacherous.

341
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,640
There must be something fishy going on.

342
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,200
My cousin

343
