367
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:56,960
Such terrifying love

368
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:58,590
will only make you

369
00:24:58,590 --> 00:24:59,920
more despicable

370
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:01,400
and annoying.

371
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:02,920
In the end,

372
00:25:03,870 --> 00:25:05,000
everything you love

373
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:07,270
and long for

374
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,590
