00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:47,200
Why do you ask?

455
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,100
Don't you know?

456
00:31:51,170 --> 00:31:52,700
And if I did know, what then?

457
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:55,240
Does

458
00:31:56,170 --> 00:31:57,160
this outsider of

459
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,020
